title: Yavapai women's soccer cannot complete comeback in final game of season | Sports | dcourier.com
text:
The Yavapai Women’s Soccer team has completed its 2025 regular season, and lost to No. 12 Eastern Arizona at home.
Unfortunately, this loss has kicked them out of playoff contention, putting an end to the team’s 2025 season.
